3 types of control flow statements

1.Decision making Statements
        - if
          a). simple if
          b). If-else
          c). Nested If
        - switch
           -executes one statement from multiple condition
           -works with byte,short,int,long(till java 6)
           -works with String(from java 7)
2.Loop statments
        - for Loop
          a). simple for loop
          b). Nested for loop
        - for each loop
        - while Loop
        - do while Loop

3.Jump statements
        - break statement
        - continue statement
